text: The Minas Gerais spinythumb frog, Bokermann's spinythumb frog or the Bokermann's stream froglet (Crossodactylus trachystomus) is a frog. It lives in Minas Gerais, Brazil. People have seen it between 60 and 1060 meters above sea level. ==References== Category:Frogs of South America
title: Crossodactylus trachystomus
